#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:1
msgid "E4206"
msgstr "E4206"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:3
msgid "Compiler diagnostic name: `must_implement_one`."
msgstr "编译器诊断名称：`must_implement_one`。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:5
msgid ""
"Traits can use `#must_implement_one` to require each implementation to "
"provide at least one method explicitly. When the attribute lists method "
"names, an implementation must define at least one of those listed "
"methods; inherited default implementations are not enough."
msgstr ""
"trait 可以使用 `#must_implement_one` 要求每个实现至少显式提供一个方法。当该"
"属性列出方法名时，实现必须定义这些方法中的至少一个；仅继承默认实现并不满足"
"要求。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:10
msgid "Erroneous example"
msgstr "错误示例"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:12
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"type Store\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"#must_implement_one(load, save)\n"
"pub(open) trait Persist {\n"
"  load(Self) -> String = _\n"
"  save(Self, String) -> Unit = _\n"
"  reset(Self) -> Unit = _\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with load(_) {\n"
"  \"cached\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with save(_, _) {\n"
"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with reset(_) {\n"
"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub impl Persist for Store with reset(_) {\n"
"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:16
msgid "Suggestion"
msgstr "建议"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:18
msgid "Implement at least one method named by `#must_implement_one`."
msgstr "实现 `#must_implement_one` 指定的至少一个方法。"

#: ../../language/error_codes/E4206.md:20
msgid ""
"///|\n"
"type Store\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"#must_implement_one(load, save)\n"
"pub(open) trait Persist {\n"
"  load(Self) -> String = _\n"
"  save(Self, String) -> Unit = _\n"
"  reset(Self) -> Unit = _\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with load(_) {\n"
"  \"cached\"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with save(_, _) {\n"
"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"impl Persist with reset(_) {\n"
"\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"///|\n"
"pub impl Persist for Store with load(_) {\n"
"  \"local\"\n"
"}\n"
msgstr ""

